ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce de East Angus et Région CHANGE NAME / BOUNDARIES
PrecisApproval for the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DE EAST ANGUS ET RÉGION, in Quebec (a) to change its name to the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DU HAUT-SAINT-FRANÇOIS; and (b) to change the boundaries of its district to Ascot Corner, Bury, Chartierville, Cookshire-Eaton, East-Angus, Hampden, La Patrie, Newport, Scotstown, Saint-Isidore-de-Clifton and the Township of Westbury.
